I’m currently in line to get my #COVID19 #vaccine @CedarsSinai. 🤗. But it’s a sad & sobering event. About 50 #healthcareheroes ahead of me, standing patiently, quietly in line. It looks like a food line😢— so long it’s winding outside the hospital building.😱
